THE National Executive Council (IDU USA NEC) and members of the Ibadan Descendants’ Union, United States of America (IDU) USA, have commiserated with the governor and Oyo State people over the death of ex-governor Abiola Ajimobi. A statement at the weekend by the National Public Relations Officer of the union, Ade Oyejobi, said that Senator Ajimobi would be remembered for his passion for infrastructural development. “Senator Ajimobi’s family and the people of Oyo State are in our prayers this time. May his soul rest in peace”, IDU USA National President Dr. Olubunmi Afonja said. 